{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/EngHeader1.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/ContentZombie2c.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by the horror classics of the 90s and 2000s,\u00a0LAPSO\u00a0brings back the oppressive atmosphere and mechanics that defined the genre.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With modern controls and an over-the-shoulder third-person camera, the classic experience gets a contemporary touch without losing the essence of <strong>true survival horror</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/ContentPuzzle1.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES &amp; UNLOCK DOORS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use keys, codes, and logic to solve puzzles that respect the player's intelligence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse wisely through a maze of doors and claustrophic corridors, through a tightly crafted interconnected map (in a &quot;metroidvania&quot; style).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MANAGE SCARCE RESOURCES &amp; MAKE TOUGH DECISIONS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a tight inventory and limited resources, every moment in the game is a difficult choice. Will you fight or flee?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Save your progress and store items in safe rooms.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/EngHeader2.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/ContentAndando1b.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A research facility plunged into chaos. In a dystopian world, a mysterious metallic substance spreads, consuming both flesh and sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What was meant to be a groundbreaking extraction experiment now demands its price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/extras/ContentZombie1d.gif?t=1739190673\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNCOVER A MYSTERY REVEALED IN FRAGMENTS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Figure out the narrative on your own through documents and clever environmental storytelling.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ESCAPE THE METALLIC CORRUPTION</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Walls that bleed steel, unexplainable creatures\u2026 and something worse lurking below.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3510530?t=1739190673","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3510530?t=1739190673","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/322fa9fe95298b0aaf8116abb4a35bd2cb4f1aed/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739190673","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510530/322fa9fe95298b0aaf8116abb4a35bd2cb4f1aed/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739190673","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akam